# Running IMDb Top 1000 Movie Dashboard
## Preview
![IMDb Dashboard Preview](assets/visualisation.png)
To run program (Windows):
-
- Create a virtual environment on directory by running: **python -m venv venv**
- Activate virtual environment by running: **venv/Scripts/Activate**
- Install dependencies (numpy library, plotly, etc) by running: **pip install -r requirements.txt**
- Now run flask app: **python dashboard.py**
- Navigate to browser and open: **http://127.0.0.1:8050/**

Dashboard now displayed
